IP geolocation
--------------
This product includes IP geolocation data created by DB-IP
(https://db-ip.com), the "IP to Country Lite" database, licensed under the
Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0):
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The bundled database (/usr/share/GeoIP/dbip-country-lite.mmdb) is used to map
peer IP addresses to country flags. You may replace it with your own MaxMind
GeoLite2-Country database via the insight.geoip_db config setting.
